### dashboard/
```
react react-dom
vite @vitejs/plugin-react
typescript
tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer
recharts
framer-motion
lucide-react
```

### server/
```
express
typescript ts-node
@mistralai/mistralai      # Mistral SDK
